Hello this is our BM102 C# programming lecture project. Our aim is early diagnosis and tracking test proccess for Covid-19 Of course we dont give accurate dna test result but comparing symptoms and giving people should go to hospital or stay at home and take care.
It was fun project for us. We hope you like either.
